Articles.Content: Jeb won the lottery recently, and before his greedy uncle could get his mitts on the money he decided to go ahead and fund a Deep Space Warp Ship, even though our top scientists assured Jeb that just because Warp was in the name doesn\'t mean it will go faster. Nevertheless those top scientists are hard at work making an engine to power this thing across the stars, *cough*harv*cough but for now it sits in a parking orbit acting as a space station.

Oh lord, I can\'t even remember which parts belong to which packs. I have 710 parts in my part folder. Yeah, I like mods. If you point out the specific part you were wondering about I may be able to remember.
